11:38.959 --> 11:48.560
cubit is in the state zero. So UF for F2 is just a C knot on Q0 and Q1. The C

100
11:48.560 --> 11:56.800
knot gate will do nothing to the first term since the control cubit is in the state zero. But on the second term, this

